Ability: Intelligence.Requires Training: Yes.Classes: All.Spellcraft is used to identify spells being cast by other spellcasters.Check: A successful check means that the character has identified a spell being cast by an opponent. The DC of this check is equal to 15 + spell level. The character also gains a +1 bonus for every 5 ranks in this skill to all saving throws against spells. Special: A specialist wizard gets a +2 bonus when dealing with a spell from his specialized school. Use: Spellcraft checks are automatic whenever a spell is cast nearby.